               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Tazkāra maṣḥafa saʿātāt “Commemoration of the Horologium” (fols.
                     1v-2r)&#xD; II) Computation tables for the hours of each month (fols. 2v-3v, 6r)&#xD;
                     - tables for the months Ṭǝrr-Maggābit (fol. 2v)&#xD; - tables for the months
                     Miyāzyā-Sane (fol. 3r)&#xD; - tables for the months Ḥamle-Maskaram (fol.
                     3v)&#xD; - tables for the months Ṭǝqǝmt-Ṗagʷǝmen (fol. 6r)&#xD; &#xD; Additio
                     1.</summary>
